1. *Ser* je prelep dan. (It is a beautiful day.)
2. *Ser*ivanje je njegovo omiljeno zanimanje. (Serving is his favorite occupation.)
3. On voli da *ser*uje svojim prijateljima. (He likes to serve his friends.)
4. Ona je *ser*ila hranu gostima. (She served food to the guests.)
5. Oni su se *ser*ivali jedni drugima. (They were serving each other.)